## FAQ

### Q: What can I learn about plasticity from your dataset? What plasticity-related data is available on the platform?

There is currently no plasticity logic implemented in the platform data/model stack, so plasticity-specific datasets or plasticity analysis outputs are not available at this time.

If helpful, offer adjacent alternatives (for example: morphology, electrophysiology, ion channels, connectivity, or neuron density data) and ask whether the user wants help with one of those.
